## Architecture

This agent uses:
- **@openai/agents**: OpenAI Agents SDK for TypeScript
- **tool() helper**: Defines tools with proper Zod schemas
- **streaming**: Real-time token streaming for responses
- **tsx**: Fast TypeScript execution for ES modules
